page.title: 20Credits
page.content: Mrs Peters and Mr Edlington (class teachers) wish to record their thanks to the following people who have so generously given of their time and expertise to this project:- Mr.L.R.Clemerson, (Headmaster). Mrs.J.Beaton, Mrs.P.Middleton,Mrs. White, Mrs.M.Bend, Mrs.T.Milne, Mr.M.Bend and Mr.F.Dawson. (Parents and friends of the school.). Rev.Evan.R.Harris. Mr.Islip. (British Rail). Mr and Mrs.A.V.Sheardown. (Farmer). The children of classes 5 and 6 Barrowby C.of E.(Controlled) Primary School. And the many other people who have helped in various ways.
